Talk, not talk. Listen, not listen.

03:14.480 --> 03:17.927
Maybe tell some stories,
go for a walk, or uh...

03:18.080 --> 03:20.080
You know, I'm kinda hoping
you're gonna say no here

03:20.120 --> 03:22.480
- so I can stop doing this, all right?
- No. Thanks, though.

03:33.520 --> 03:38.321
- I feel so shitty.
- I know, man. I know. I'm sorry.

